<item>
            <title>[LU-19571] Make checkpatch post only first 100 warnings back to Gerrit</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19571</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have patchsets with thousands of comments made by wc-checkpatch. This is seriously overloading Gerrit without any sense as I do not believe if anyone reads them in&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/57777&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/57777&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62211&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62211&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62087&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62087&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61789&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61789&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Solution: post only first 100 comments or put -1 for a patchset.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
